## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d802b-102">에 대 한 입력된 모드를 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 에 의해 결정 됩니다 해당 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d802b-102">The input mode for an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> is determined by its <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d802b-103">기본 입력된 모드는 문법을 정의한 나타내는 음성은 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 음성 입력와 일치 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d802b-103">The default input mode is Voice, which indicates that the grammar defined by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> will match speech input.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d802b-104">Dtmf 모드는 문법을 이중 톤 Multi-frequency () dtmf 음성 대신 일치 됩니다 것을 나타냅니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d802b-104">The Dtmf mode indicates that a grammar will match Dual-Tone Multi-Frequency (DTMF) tones instead of speech.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d802b-105">12는 대부분의 전화기에서 흔히 발견 되 16 dtmf 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d802b-105">There are 16 DTMF tones, 12 of which are commonly found on most telephones.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d802b-106">만들 때를 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 에서 개체를 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>의 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 개체에서 지정 된 입력의 형식과 일치 합니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> 속성의 인스턴스를 가져옵니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarMode>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d802b-106">When you create a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object from an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object will match the type of input specified by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> property, which gets an instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarMode>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
string srgsDocumentFile = Path.Combine(Path.GetTempPath(), "srgsDocumentFile.xml");  
SrgsDocument document = null;  
GrammarBuilder builder = null;  
Grammar grammar = null;  
  
Choices firstThree = new Choices(new string[] {"1", "2", "3"});  
Choices nextThree = new Choices(new string[] {"4", "5", "6"});  
Choices lastThree = new Choices(new string[] {"7", "8", "9"});  
  
Choices keyPadChoices = new Choices(new GrammarBuilder[] {firstThree, nextThree, lastThree, new Choices("0")});  
  
builder = new GrammarBuilder(keyPadChoices);  
document = new SrgsDocument(builder);  
  
document.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Dtmf;  
grammar = new Grammar(document);   
```
